## Change Control Workflow

- [ ] 1. Log the change: Document the request formally with date, requestor, and description
- [ ] 2. Assess impact: Evaluate impact on timeline, budget, resources, and quality
- [ ] 3. Quantify cost: Estimate additional time, cost, and resource impact
- [ ] 4. Get approval: Route to appropriate decision-maker (client or internal)
- [ ] 5. Communicate: Inform all stakeholders of approved changes
- [ ] 6. Update baseline: Adjust project plan, schedule, and budget
- [ ] 7. Implement: Execute the change and track it

## Key Inputs
- Change description: {{change_description}}
- Requestor: {{requestor}}
- Current project status: {{project_status}}
- Impact assessment: {{impact_assessment}}
